The paper focuses on generating questions from images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The use of variational autoencoders and long short-term memory networks also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
